<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>GitHub contribution checker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.1.1/css/bootstrap.css">
    <style media="screen">
      .container {
        max-width: 730px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">

      <div class="page-header text-center">
        <h1>GitHub Contribution Checker</h1>

        <p class="lead">
          So, you want to check if some GitHub contributions will be counted for you?
          <br>
          Step right up and use the input box below to specify the commit URL!
        </p>

        <form class="form" role="form" method="get">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input class="form-control span6" name="url" placeholder="https://github.com/:user/:repo/commit/:sha">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
